  "about_text": {
    "type": "text",
    "value": "Founded in 1998 in the heart of Kerala, Golden Spark Jewellery has been a trusted name in fine jewellery for over two decades. We blend traditional craftsmanship with contemporary design, creating pieces that are as unique as the people who wear them."
  },
  "about_text_2": {
    "type": "text",
    "value": "Every ring, necklace, bracelet, and earring that leaves our workshop carries the mark of our master artisans — each trained in age-old techniques, each devoted to perfection in every curve and facet."
